race.comment: OVERLAND BOY (8) was in the placings last time but three back posted a slick 29.49 win over 515m at Sandown. Should be in this for a long way. TWISTED FANTASY (1) goes very well this trip starting 16 times for six wins and three minors. Comes off a (25.35) win last time, scoring by 2.5 lengths in a Grade 5 over 450m at Ballarat. Looks one of the chances. FURIOSO RICK (3) has a strong record here with four wins and four placings from 11 starts. Placed last time (19.01) at Healesville in a Free For All, finishing second and beaten 2.25 lengths. With even luck and a clean start can sneak into the finish. CAPRICORN ONE (6) has strong credentials at this circuit over this journey.
